!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{ :charset => "UTF-8" }
  %body
    %ul
      %li
        %strong Project:
        = link_to @project_name, @project_url
      %li
        %strong Organization:
        = link_to @organization_name, @organization_url
      %li
        %strong Project URL:
        = @project_url
    %hr
    %p
      %strong= @comment_author
      made the following comment:
    %p= @comment
    - if @comment_source and @comment_source != "Comment"
      %p= "Link: #{@comment_source}"
    %hr
    %p{ :style => "color: #ccc" } You can change your notification preferences on the project page.
